item.title: Falcon - Insomniac
item.dc:creator: anon86704580
item.description:
Cool melody! Drums are a bit too… fast? The snare hits too quickly I mean imo. Cool chords! Neat Instrument choice! The “Bewm” is a cool effect! A bit repetitive, but they may be what you were going for, idk. If not, I’d switch up the drums a bit

Uniqueness: 7/10
Predictability: 6/10
Use of Instruments/Automation/Samples: 6/10
Complexity: 7/10
Feeling: 7/10

Overall: 33/50 Keep up the awesomeness!
